> Hydras smiled evilish and commanded Darkhawk to hunt Tucson and his friends, he started to trackdown his old nemesis Rodimus Prime. Kup arrived to the area where Tucson was and he opened fire against Scouge and Scorponok.

As Cyclonus and the others ran along with Hydras Cyclonus got a
communication from Jhiaxus, and he smiled.

"Sir." Cyclonus said, "I believe we have most of them cornered in one
spot, including Rodimus!" Cyclonus picked up the pace, "This way!"
